pkg mgt show notes:

Installing pacaur (yaourt helper)
Install the key:
sudo gpg --recv-keys --keyserver hkp://pgp.mit.edu 1EB2638FF56C0C53
Install pacaur:
yaourt -S cower-git pacaur-git
Pacaur usage:
pacaur -S <package names>

Downgrading a package:
yaourt -S downgrade
sudo pacman -S expac
Command to see recent upgraded packages:
expac --timefmt='%Y-%m-%d %T' '%l\t%n' | sort | tail -50
sudo downgrade <package name>  Then pick the version you want to roll back to.

Links:
